Replace these placeholders when creating new Living Software hooks:
- `[hook-name]`: Actual hook name (kebab-case)
- `[HookClassName]`: Pascal case class name
- `[hook-type]`: Hook trigger type
- `[autonomy-level]`: Level of autonomous operation
- `[configOption1]`, `[configOption2]`: Hook-specific config options
- `[defaultValue]`: Default configuration values

